238
00:13:49,393 --> 00:13:50,394
Why?

239
00:13:52,832 --> 00:13:54,050
Because he meets Mozart.

240
00:13:55,269 --> 00:14:01,449
And he realizes that he'll never
be able to compete with this wild,

241
00:14:02,363 --> 00:14:07,934
