242
00:14:08,935 --> 00:14:12,634
So, Brett was
Salieri and Kevin was Mozart?

243
00:14:17,857 --> 00:14:21,077
Maybe in college, a little bit.

244
00:14:21,556 --> 00:14:24,472
He was talented, but obviously I
don't feel that way

245
